117
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,900
What if there really was a secret
and she got everything?

118
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:20,890
That would've been bad.

119
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:22,950
You should be working
at the inspection agency.

120
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:25,240
You should let me be
the Chief Inspector.

121
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,600
