125
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,290
I was afraid you'd be caught
by Shen Miaoyi.

126
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:39,870
Anyway, you were there.

127
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,720
I would protect you.

128
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,630
Xinglan? Xinglan?

129
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,950
Young Master,

130
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:25,160
